OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FA public inquiry into urology services
OL,7,Fat the Southern Health and Social Care
OL,8,FTrust has found there were significant
OL,9,Frisks to patient safety and some were
OL,10,F"seriously harmed".
OL,12,FThe Urology Services Inquiry was
OL,13,Festablished by former Health Minister
OL,14,FRobin Swann in March 2021 after
OL,15,Fconcerns were raised about the work of
OL,16,FAidan O'Brien.
OL,18,FThe consultant urologist worked at
OL,19,FCraigavon Area Hospital for 28 years
OL,20,Fand retired in July 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FOver 1,000 of his patients were
OL,7,Frecalled between January 2019 and June
OL,8,F2020 after a number of serious adverse
OL,9,Fincidents were raised by the trust.
OL,11,FThe inquiry found Mr O'Brien was a
OL,12,Fskilled surgeon and he was not
OL,13,Fsupported adequately by the trust.
OL,15,FThe Urology Services Inquiry, "is not
OL,16,Fsimply about one doctor" and
OL,17,Fidentified "systemic" causes of harm
OL,18,Fin the Southern Health and Social Care
OL,19,FTrust, chairwoman Christine Smith KC
OL,20,Fhas said.
OL,26,@wD@_OUxD@XO]yD@LOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FMs Smith said: "The way Mr O'Brien
OL,7,Fcarried out his practice and his
OL,8,Ffollow-up processes were unsafe.
OL,9,FFailure to consistently follow
OL,10,Fevidence-based guidelines for
OL,11,Ftreatment, delayed or absent triage,
OL,12,Ffailures to review investigation
OL,13,Fresults promptly, non-dictation of
OL,14,Fletters, poor record keeping, and
OL,15,Fretention of notes outside the
OL,16,Fhospital created direct risks to
OL,17,Fpatients and undermined continuity of
OL,18,Fcare.
OL,26,@nD@POU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,F"While Mr O'Brien bears responsibility
OL,7,Ffor how he operated his practice, the
OL,8,Freality is that the trust processes
OL,9,Fwere insufficiently robust to identify
OL,10,For deal with the risk that any
OL,11,Fshortcomings in this practice
OL,12,Fpresented to patient safety."
OL,14,FShe added: "It failed to recognise
OL,15,Fthat what were termed administrative
OL,16,Ffailings could be indicative of wider
OL,17,Fproblems with serious consequences.
OL,18,FThese were not investigated, and
OL,19,Fultimately patients were harmed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@]O]vD@LOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FMs Smith further stated: "Our central
OL,7,Ffinding is that the deeper causes of
OL,8,Fharm were systemic ` weak governance,
OL,9,Fpoor oversight, ineffective
OL,10,Fescalation, and underdeveloped
OL,11,Fleadership created the conditions in
OL,12,Fwhich patients could come to harm. Put
OL,13,Fsimply, this was a failure to
OL,14,Frecognise risk early or respond to it
OL,15,Fproperly."
OL,17,FThe inquiry identified systemic
OL,18,Ffailures in governance, oversight,
OL,19,Fleadership, culture and board
OL,20,Faccountability.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FPatients suffered serious harm,
OL,7,Fincluding failures in diagnosis,
OL,8,Ftreatment and follow up.
OL,10,FThere were also repeated missed
OL,11,Fopportunities to act on Mr O'Brien,
OL,12,Fwho the inquiry said did not set out
OL,13,Fto cause harm but described as "in
OL,14,Fdifficulty".
OL,16,FRisks were not addressed and there
OL,17,Fwere weak systems which failed to
OL,18,Fidentify and act on risk early.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FThe report detailed three
OL,7,Frecommendations to ensure patient
OL,8,Fsafety, strengthen leadership and
OL,9,Fimprove use of data to identify and
OL,10,Fact on risk.
OL,12,FChair of the Inquiry, Christine Smith
OL,13,FKC said the report focused on patients
OL,14,Fwho were "badly let down" by the
OL,15,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,F"They faced delays in diagnosis and
OL,7,Ftreatment, including cancer care, poor
OL,8,Fcommunication, and too often they were
OL,9,Fleft without the clear, high-quality,
OL,10,Ftimely interventions they should have
OL,11,Fexpected."
OL,13,F"Weak governance, poor oversight,
OL,14,Fineffective escalation and
OL,15,Funderdeveloped leadership created the
OL,16,Fconditions in which patients could
OL,17,Fcome to harm. There was a failure to
OL,18,Frecognise risk early and to respond to
OL,19,Fit properly."
OL,26,@{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FThe inquiry found that Mr O'Brien was
OL,7,Fa skilled surgeon who did not set out
OL,8,Fto cause harm, however the trust
OL,9,Ffailed to recognise that he was a
OL,10,Fdoctor "in difficulty" and failed to
OL,11,Fmanage him appropriately.
OL,13,FWhile Mr O'Brien was the catalyst for
OL,14,Fthe inquiry, the report highlights
OL,15,Ffailings were "deep rooted" across the
OL,16,Ftrust.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FMs Smith KC added: "Issues about Mr
OL,7,FO'Brien's practice were known for
OL,8,Fyears, but they were never
OL,9,Fsatisfactorily addressed. Warning
OL,10,Fsigns were missed, and opportunities
OL,11,Fto act were not taken soon enough.
OL,13,F"It highlights wider systemic
OL,14,Ffailings, where risks were not
OL,15,Fescalated, concerns were not acted
OL,16,Fupon, and opportunities to prevent
OL,17,Fharm were missed across the trust.
OL,19,F"Stronger systems of governance would
OL,20,Fhave enabled earlier detection and
OL,21,Fmore effective intervention."
OL,26,@nD@TOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FWeaknesses in governance, leadership
OL,7,Fand culture included undue deference
OL,8,Fto seniority, professionals working in
OL,9,Fsilos, and failures of medical
OL,10,Fleadership across a range of levels
OL,11,Fwho were not aligned around a clear
OL,12,Fand consistent focus on delivering
OL,13,Fsafe, high-quality care.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FThe report found that the board did
OL,7,Fnot fully understand or discharge its
OL,8,Fresponsibilities and did not
OL,9,Fadequately fulfil its role in driving
OL,10,Fculture, strategy and improvement.
OL,11,FThere was no effective assurance
OL,12,Fconcerning the quality of care, and
OL,13,Finsufficient challenge or critical
OL,14,Foversight.
OL,16,FThe inquiry recognises that
OL,17,Fimprovements have been made including
OL,18,Fchanges within the trust and work led
OL,19,Fby the Department of Health.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
