PN,41113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782310728
OL,3,CUrology inquiry finds patients
OL,4,C'seriously harmed'
OL,6,FHowever, it said further, sustained
OL,7,Fand transformational change is
OL,8,Frequired.
